  Made fontconfig 2.4 patch be applied only if fontconfig >=2.4 is actually installed.
  Added some magic sed to fix bug #157002.

  07 Jan 2007; Michele Noberasco <s4t4n@gentoo.org> adesklets-0.6.1-r1.ebuild,
  adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Made adesklets create log files in user home directories instead of /tmp.
  See bug #160132.

*adesklets-0.6.1-r1 (20 Nov 2006)

  20 Nov 2006; Michele Noberasco <s4t4n@gentoo.org> +adesklets-0.6.1-r1.ebuild:
  Revision bump. Added patch to use fontconfig >= 2.4. See bug #148988. Also,
  made fontconfig support optional and revisited package dependancies. See bug #150669.
  adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Revisited package dependancies. See bug #150669.

  30 Aug 2006; Michele Noberasco <s4t4n@gentoo.org> adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Moved xwifinfo dep to fix bug #128018 again.
  adesklets-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Wiped out older version.

  18 Aug 2006; Michael Cummings <mcummings@gentoo.org>
  adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Marking amd64 stable

  31 Jul 2006; Michele Noberasco <s4t4n@gentoo.org> adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Added call to fixlocalpod to fix bug #142169.

  27 Jul 2006; Michele Noberasco <s4t4n@gentoo.org> adesklets-0.5.0.ebuild:
  Added yet another modular X dep.
  adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Added patch to fix bug #131813.
  Bumped up python version requirement to fix bug #132031.
  Fixed python and perl script building. Closes bug #131675.
  Stable for x86, closing bug #140771.

  30 Apr 2006; Sven Blumenstein <bazik@gentoo.org> adesklets-0.6.1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword.

